### Mandatory Source Headers
To maintain the integrity of the project and ensure clear ownership, **every single source file** 
in this repository must contain the following header at the very top. Any Pull Request (PR) 
submitted without this header will be automatically rejected.

```text
Copyright (c) 2026 Neil Talap and/or its designated Affiliates.
Licensed under the Dragonfly Public License v1.0 (DPL-1.0).
See the LICENSE file in the project root for full terms.
```
